    "任一所选 App 启动 → 自动连接；全部退出 → 自动断开（只断开由自动连接拉起的会话，手动开启的 VPN 不受影响）。iPhone/iPad 上可用「快捷指令 → 自动化 → App」实现同样效果。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Any selected app launching → auto-connect; all quitting → auto-disconnect (only sessions started by auto-connect; a VPN you started manually is never touched). On iPhone/iPad, use Shortcuts → Automation → App for the same effect."
          }
        }
      }
    },
