    "检测到系统代理已开启（%@，可能是 Clash 等工具）。轻舟是 TUN 模式，可与它共存（会形成冗余的双重代理，一般不影响使用）；若个别 App 联网异常，可先关掉系统代理排除干扰。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "A system proxy is enabled (%@, likely a tool such as Clash). Qingzhou runs in TUN mode and can coexist with it (this forms a redundant double-proxy chain, usually harmless). If certain apps fail to connect, turn off the system proxy to rule out interference."
          }
        }
      }
    },
